262
00:17:56,420 --> 00:17:58,600
Do you have any of your work with you?

263
00:17:58,600 --> 00:18:00,110
Yes, sir.

264
00:18:03,930 --> 00:18:06,140
- Here they are.
- Great.

265
00:18:12,290 --> 00:18:14,900
Kuzuya, was it?

266
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,820
Yes, sir.

267
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:19,060
