432
00:30:24,090 --> 00:30:27,090
â™ª <i>Is it the search you're looking for?</i> â™ª

433
00:30:27,090 --> 00:30:30,050
â™ª <i>Be it in a bag, or your desk</i> â™ª

434
00:30:30,050 --> 00:30:33,370
Nari takes the stage!

435
00:30:33,370 --> 00:30:36,530
â™ª <i>I still feel inclined to keep looking</i> â™ª

436
00:30:36,530 --> 00:30:39,800
â™ª <i>But for now, how about a dance with me?</i> â™ª

